            <h1 class="font-lora font-bold mb-4" style="color:#faf7f4">African Grey Parrot Talking Ability: How Well Do They Really Talk?</h1>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color:rgba(250,247,244,0.85)">Not "1,000 words on day one." Here's the honest version — what they really say, when it starts, and Maxy, one of our Congos, doing it on camera.</p>
